&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary day-to-day point of contact for a defined portfolio of edtech partners, proactively managing relationships and ensuring partner health.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end onboarding experience for new edtech partners following agreement and contracting, ensuring smooth technical and relational ramp-up with clear milestones and timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct regular check-ins and business reviews to assess partner progress, surface challenges, and identify opportunities to deepen engagement with Learning Commons&#39; infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor partner usage and integration health; flag risks early and develop action plans to address them in collaboration with product and engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;

